				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BB%ABa-%C3%82n/B%E1%BA%A3o-Ninh-S%C3%B9ng-Ph%C3%BAc-t%E1%BB%B1-bi/poem-yadLYWXRS0UtV15FauZxIQ">Bảo Ninh Sùng Phúc tự bi - 保寧崇福寺碑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BB%ABa-%C3%82n/author-d8MSBkSrQsUgYbCqr0kX5g">Lý Thừa Ân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-H%E1%BB%AFu-H%E1%BA%A1nh-ca-c%C6%A1-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-ni-c%C3%B4-c%C3%A0-sa-ti%E1%BB%83u-%E1%BA%A3nh/poem-l1sNFceP37vhG7t1_CL5cA">Đề Hữu Hạnh ca cơ trước ni cô cà sa tiểu ảnh - 題有幸歌姬著尼姑袈裟小影</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng/%C4%90%C3%ACnh-th%C3%AD-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-s%C3%A1ch/poem-rF91EB30-zT6DtZAE4A1yw">Đình thí đối sách - 廷試對策</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng/author-GfNq85EUzTvOO-A-Y5zO9w">Phan Đình Phùng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/H%E1%BA%A1-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-Wgt7w2bSjWJuGnqE1f8Ufw">Hạ nhật ngẫu thành kỳ 1 - 夏日偶成其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Khu-xa-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-m%C3%B4n/poem-tCpC2pCWvzbWdChYE_74fg">Khu xa thướng đông môn - 驅車上東門</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/M%E1%BA%A1n-th%C3%A0nh-I-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-5jDf172ALweEFEa6mOYi0w">Mạn thành (I) kỳ 1 - 漫成其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/M%C3%B4-ng%C6%B0-nhi-Thu%E1%BA%A7n-Hy-K%E1%BB%B7-H%E1%BB%A3i-t%E1%BB%B1-H%E1%BB%93-B%E1%BA%AFc-t%C3%A0o-di-H%E1%BB%93-Nam-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-quan-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%ADnh-Chi-tr%C3%AD-t%E1%BB%ADu-ti%E1%BB%83u-s%C6%A1n-%C4%91%C3%ACnh/poem-ijTBG5iB_tnSCeJXzNX9Hw">Mô ngư nhi - Thuần Hy Kỷ Hợi, tự Hồ Bắc tào di Hồ Nam, đồng quan Vương Chính Chi trí tửu tiểu sơn đình, vi phú - 摸魚兒－淳熙己亥，自湖北漕移湖南，同官王正之置酒小山亭，為賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%A3o-ph%C3%A1t/poem-QTVFJ9Z0-BPrKIIARvfJrA">Tảo phát - 早發</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Th%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-9FKmL1Im7h6fUCA3uVboGg">Thất tịch - 七夕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/Tr%E1%BB%AB-t%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-0FUoqqh7D8aLj4boJLIO_w">Trừ tịch - 除夕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/author-mhAlF-W1JHQDMsH_S0aV3Q">Hà Như</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
